=A Fleeting Dream=

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:08.360
=Episode 1=

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:20.530
(Lian Xinruo,
eldest daughter of the Lian family)

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:26.450
Why?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.719
(Lian Zhong,
second branch of the Lian family)

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:30.450
Why?

00:01:30.759 --> 00:01:32.289
My dear niece.

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.330
Go down and keep your father company.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.450
Father!

00:01:37.759 --> 00:01:40.049
Father, save me!

00:01:41.279 --> 00:01:42.529
No!

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:48.729
Bury her.

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:55.319
(Lian Zhong)

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.769
(Lian Xinya, daughter of Lian Zhong)
Lian Xinya.

00:01:58.319 --> 00:02:00.449
(If I make it out alive,)

00:02:01.559 --> 00:02:04.489
(I'll make you pay in blood.)

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:09.650
(Five years later)

00:02:14.559 --> 00:02:15.929
(It's been five years.)

00:02:16.359 --> 00:02:17.889
(I've finally returned.)

00:02:26.940 --> 00:02:27.959
(Pei Yuze)

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:30.440
(Second branch of the Pei family)
I heard Lian family only sent Lian Zhong.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:34.970
The business tycoon of Hu City
will fall tonight.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.210
That's amusing.

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:43.290
Well?

00:02:43.759 --> 00:02:44.889
Do I look good?

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:47.610
The tricks I taught you

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.370
aren't meant to be used on me.

00:03:10.519 --> 00:03:11.689
What now?

00:03:12.279 --> 00:03:13.449
Falling for me?

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:15.130
Don't worry.

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:17.889
Help me take my revenge,

00:03:18.359 --> 00:03:21.849
and I'll make sure
you get your brother's life

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:24.089
and the position of
the Pei family's head.

00:03:26.279 --> 00:03:27.249
Let's go.

00:03:28.440 --> 00:03:30.210
It's time for Hu City to liven up.

00:03:37.420 --> 00:03:40.940
(Happiness)

00:03:44.170 --> 00:03:45.798
(Jiang Yao,
godson to the Pei family's head)

00:03:45.799 --> 00:03:48.169
Yao, why are you here?

00:03:48.220 --> 00:03:50.159
(Pei Xueshan)

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:51.600
(Daughter of Pei Yujie)
Socializing is exhausting.

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:53.329
I'm hiding here to laze around.

00:03:54.119 --> 00:03:55.529
With Father away from Hu City,

00:03:55.559 --> 00:03:57.809
so it's on you to manage
the Pei family affairs.

00:03:57.880 --> 00:03:58.969
You've worked hard.

00:04:00.079 --> 00:04:01.689
I'm your fiancé.

00:04:01.839 --> 00:04:02.959
We're family.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:04.530
These are my responsibilities.

00:04:05.880 --> 00:04:08.210
Who knows what Du Youmeng is capable of,

00:04:08.359 --> 00:04:11.289
but she's got Second Master Pei
rushing the engagement,

00:04:12.079 --> 00:04:14.729
and the whole Pei family
hasn't even met her.

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:15.969
It's ridiculous.

00:04:16.480 --> 00:04:19.038
I heard that Second Master Pei can only
inherit some of the family's businesses

00:04:19.039 --> 00:04:21.009
after getting married.

00:04:21.039 --> 00:04:23.929
Everyone knows Pei Yuze
isn't going to live past thirty.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.839
I bet Du Youmeng's marrying him

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:26.798
just for the inheritance.

00:04:26.799 --> 00:04:28.929
Please welcome the guest of honor.

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.489
Xin...

00:04:53.599 --> 00:04:54.969
Xinruo!

00:04:56.020 --> 00:04:57.679
(Happiness)

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.838
Welcome, everyone,
to my engagement banquet with Youmeng.

00:05:00.839 --> 00:05:01.479
Today...

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:02.370
You...

00:05:02.519 --> 00:05:04.249
I thought you were dead!

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:12.770
Mr. Lian, what do you mean?

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:15.358
Cursing my fiancée in public?

00:05:15.359 --> 00:05:17.529
Lian Xinruo is still alive.

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:20.159
Wasn't she dating Jiang Yao before?

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:22.490
Why is she engaged to
Second Master Pei now?

00:05:22.559 --> 00:05:24.920
- First love turns into Second Aunt.
- First love turns into Second Aunt.

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.409
This is going to be interesting.

00:05:28.599 --> 00:05:30.318
Second Master, please forgive me.

00:05:30.319 --> 00:05:31.239
It's just that

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:34.118
Miss Du looks so much like
my late niece.

00:05:34.119 --> 00:05:35.249
I couldn't control myself.

00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:36.530
My apologies.

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:38.850
Oh, I get it now.

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.439
You've mistaken me for someone else.

00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:42.879
Well, I grew up overseas.

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:45.089
This is actually my first time
in Hu City.

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.290
But with how nervous this gentleman is,

00:05:49.359 --> 00:05:52.569
could it be he did something
to wrong his niece?

00:05:55.799 --> 00:05:57.329
Miss Du, you must be joking.

00:05:57.400 --> 00:05:58.570
How could that be?

00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:04.318
Dear guests,
before the ceremony kicks off,

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:06.199
we've got a concert for you.

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:07.850
Enjoy yourselves.

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:11.570
- All right.
- All right.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:14.170
- Come on.
- This way, please.

00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:27.710
(Shanghai, Xinxin Department Store)

00:06:30.200 --> 00:06:31.210
Well.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.609
Mr. Lian.

00:06:36.039 --> 00:06:37.089
Miss Du.

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:38.809
To be honest with you.

00:06:39.400 --> 00:06:42.318
You look very much like
my deceased niece.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.729
It makes me wonder

00:06:43.839 --> 00:06:45.569
if maybe you two
are actually the same person.

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:47.999
Why do you still think I'm your niece?

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.450
I mean no offense, Miss Du.

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:53.199
My late niece was truly unfortunate.

00:06:53.200 --> 00:06:54.970
If she could really still be alive,

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:57.450
I could help my elder brother
take good care of her.

00:06:58.359 --> 00:06:58.959
Oh, right.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:01.410
My niece had a birthmark
on her lower back.

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.809
Miss Du, would you let me...

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:08.530
Help! Help!

00:07:08.799 --> 00:07:10.169
You little rascal!

00:07:10.480 --> 00:07:11.650
You really need a lesson!

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:14.050
You...

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:17.850
Lian Zhong, how dare you!

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:26.530
Don't get angry. Take care of yourself.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:28.970
I'm fine.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:30.810
Darling, are you okay?

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.889
My hand hurts so much!

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:36.010
For some reason, Boss Lian suddenly *
tried to take off my clothes.

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:41.639
I guess being away so long has made
the people in Hu City forget

00:07:41.640 --> 00:07:42.969
that I'm one of the Peis too.

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:45.210
Hence, you're acting so brazen.

00:07:45.359 --> 00:07:46.959
Second Master, don't get me wrong.
It's not...

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:48.130
Forget it.

00:07:48.799 --> 00:07:51.089
It's our engagement day today.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:53.730
No need to argue
with someone irrelevant.

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:55.850
For Youmeng's sake,

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:57.930
I'll let it go today.

00:07:58.599 --> 00:07:59.849
You're not welcome here.

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:01.969
Leave now.

00:08:02.799 --> 00:08:03.969
Mr. Lian.

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:05.610
Do you know

00:08:05.759 --> 00:08:09.729
what the smell of rain
mixed with soil is like?

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:18.530
(Rain and Soil.)

00:08:18.679 --> 00:08:20.289
Whoever you are,

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:22.970
let's see how long
you can get away with this.

00:09:22.980 --> 00:09:28.190
(Xinxin)

00:09:30.920 --> 00:09:33.410
Yuze, give me a hand
with this zipper.

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:56.999
Jiang Yao, how dare you!

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.119
Who let you into my room?

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:01.370
Miss Du, what's your purpose
in getting close to Second Master Pei?

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:06.410
My purpose?

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:09.930
You barged into an elder's room
without permission.

00:10:10.040 --> 00:10:11.490
And what's your purpose?

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:15.570
With that face, and so desperate
to marry into the Pei family,

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:18.158
is it for money or for revenge?

00:10:18.159 --> 00:10:20.449
You really have some nerve.

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:24.198
What now? You and Lian Xinruo

00:10:24.199 --> 00:10:26.238
got some dirty little secret?

00:10:26.239 --> 00:10:29.689
Lian Xinruo's father killed my father.

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:32.010
But,

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:35.129
even if you're not Lian Xinruo,

00:10:35.560 --> 00:10:36.770
with that face of yours,

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:39.129
I'm still very interested.

00:10:43.799 --> 00:10:44.649
You...

00:10:44.799 --> 00:10:45.879
What are you doing?

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:48.689
If Yuze saw us like this,

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:52.450
would he believe you, or me?

00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:02.650
Yuze, he...

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:04.369
Yao.

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:06.690
Care to explain yourself?

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:09.410
Uncle Yuze, Miss Du,
don't get me wrong.

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:11.130
I am here to tell you both

00:11:11.159 --> 00:11:13.370
that Master Pei knew nothing
about the engagement.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:16.249
And now that it's fallen through,
with Master Pei returning soon,

00:11:16.359 --> 00:11:18.010
if you two want to be together,

00:11:18.199 --> 00:11:19.449
it won't be that easy.

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:22.930
Yao, remember who you are.

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:24.970
You're only Xueshan's fiancé.

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:27.170
That doesn't make you
part of the Pei family.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.610
So when it comes to
the Pei elders' affairs,

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:31.690
you'd best not speak out of turn.

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:35.170
If that's the case,

00:11:35.520 --> 00:11:36.850
I'll take my leave.

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:50.690
You've forgotten, haven't you?

00:11:50.839 --> 00:11:54.689
Du Youmeng should hold
no hate toward Hu City.

00:11:56.319 --> 00:11:57.929
Answer me again.

00:11:58.319 --> 00:12:02.929
Du Youmeng should hold
no hate toward Hu City.

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.930
Who are you?

00:12:08.279 --> 00:12:09.649
I am...

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:16.130
I am Du Youmeng.

