♪The city night silently envelops♪

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:41.970
♪Hate and love♪

00:12:43.320 --> 00:12:49.490
♪His voice lingers by my ear♪

00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:54.399
♪In this unavoidable dead end
I encounter♪

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:59.690
♪How can wounded love burn again♪

00:12:59.800 --> 00:13:05.090
♪Leaving only his unpredictable smile♪

00:13:05.220 --> 00:13:10.199
♪My heart receives
his gentle signals drop by drop♪

00:13:10.200 --> 00:13:13.839
♪Wounded wings try to rely on♪

00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.559
♪Secret love♪

00:13:15.560 --> 00:13:21.090
♪Hidden in his most passionate embrace♪

00:13:21.480 --> 00:13:25.919
♪Ignoring the noisy lights and wine♪

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:31.319
♪Being a quiet cat in his arms♪

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:36.970
♪Entwining the rest of my life,
with no escape♪